目的,卡謬以苦難等荒謬去指責其理論<br />\n<br />\nbtw can Google 反抗者"},{"pid":"88a21a98d9f50166a8db20e49611b6335f6c6574","tid":726400,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00d96f81c61b1822483612a7f85de82df80daebd","tid":726400,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"咩叫存在?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原句於黑格爾原文出處有咩含意同論述等大家唔洗淪為鳩up之流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不情之請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6070b10394e838bed22ba603d69ff36d41100fd4","tid":726400,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86d27bc5a044650644f9b0c5e8adea2a4ced3023","tid":726400,"uid":106363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b19e99dfea6eff225a1d0922b6e5cb4805a9cc5","tid":726400,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"有因有果 存在必合因果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"量子力學否定咗因果定律"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"論學本來就無絶對 只係未被推翻"},{"pid":"8397de8bc7609dbfd1b0129cbead83000c48dc35","tid":726400,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有因有果 存在必合因果</blockquote><br />\n量子力學否定咗因果定律</blockquote><br />\nsource? 論文呢？"},{"pid":"1ad1a0e4340fc8b9f2c8b404790cd50d1c3f4a8d","tid":726400,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:07:56.000Z","msg":"我覺得係啱, 天下萬物, 會存在, 必有他存在的意義<br />\n<br />\n所謂&quot;必合理&quot;, 唔係指佢既存在一定係啱, 可以係唔啱, <br />\n但唔啱既野唔代表唔應該存在, 因為佢既存在有可能會令世界有某種改變, <br />\n<br />\n而且, 世上萬物, 要有相對至會有體現, 有苦你至覺得甜, 有善你至會感到惡, <br />\n<br />\n所以, 凡存在, 必合理, 係啱既"},{"pid":"0e79e16680a3f3155227a7f4b7bff1c7f97353c0","tid":726400,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:11:51.000Z","msg":"合唔合理係靠人定義<br />\n對香港人黎講 食人唔合理 <br />\n但對食人族黎講係合理<br />\n<br />\n某樣野既然存在，即對某部分人黎講係合理存在。"},{"pid":"4cacba871ef1b0a4d17a253c97914b5729781f2d","tid":726400,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"中共存在 合理"},{"pid":"e9d9176f22fd075b9c74c239626fc79125774abc","tid":726400,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a21a98d9f50166a8db20e49611b6335f6c6574","tid":726400,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00d96f81c61b1822483612a7f85de82df80daebd","tid":726400,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"咩叫存在?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原句於黑格爾原文出處有咩含意同論述等大家唔洗淪為鳩up之流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不情之請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://books.google.nl/books?id=bRfI1uGyHd8C&amp;pg=PA4&amp;lpg=PA4&amp;dq=黑格爾+凡存在&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=ZrNj9ad3bt&amp;sig=hlDdyE-GuYJK2UyBuMzEOHqprmw&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiA_uvI3IDcAhUluqQKHSsyAPU4PBDoAQgtMAA#v=onepage&amp;q=黑格爾%20凡存在&amp;f=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.nl%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DbRfI1uGyHd8C%26pg%3DPA4%26lpg%3DPA4%26dq%3D%E9%BB%91%E6%A0%BC%E7%88%BE%2B%E5%87%A1%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%26source%3Dbl%26ots%3DZrNj9ad3bt%26sig%3DhlDdyE-GuYJK2UyBuMzEOHqprmw%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiA_uvI3IDcAhUluqQKHSsyAPU4PBDoAQgtMAA%23v%3Donepage%26q%3D%E9%BB%91%E6%A0%BC%E7%88%BE%2520%E5%87%A1%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%26f%3Dfalse&d=nbPBpL95CC5kiLBe3I2%2Fd0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=fdc5b2e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.nl/books?id=bRfI1uGyHd8C&amp;pg=PA4&amp;lpg=PA4&amp;dq=黑格爾+凡存在&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=ZrNj9ad3bt&amp;sig=hlDdyE-GuYJK2UyBuMzEOHqprmw&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sa=X&a